{"tid":1774480,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"如果寫自己嘅操作日記，會唔會有人睇㗎?","createTime":"2019-12-08T10:11:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T08:38:16.000Z","uid":308853,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e40e20b5cfdb9923feb9c6be802d63528bfb9c83","tid":1774480,"uid":308853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T10:11:05.000Z","msg":"我意思係有操作（期權）嘅日子，寫出嚟，我冇話表演呀。因為我係期權小學一年雞，長做長輸。想寫嘅原因係想分享下個思路，我覺得基本知識我有，但實戰唔得。如果遇到有高手指點一下就最正啦。有冇人會睇會回覆呢？<br />\n<br />\n我而家針對一隻個股做緊投機性買賣，<strong>唔係</strong>short put收貨，有貨covered call。<br />\n冇涉及實貨冇得守，真係輸多贏少，呢排輸到褲甩。<br />\n<br />\n個寫法唔會寫數字咁悶，但會寫買定沽，價內定價外，到期月，升咗跌咗會寫，大約賺蝕會寫。<br />\n<br />\n有人睇嗎？"},{"pid":"45db7df0cd9e8c9de0a5bfcdd4f8dbedc81d4e46","tid":1774480,"uid":57796,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T12:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3266c0ff50edb1be903f8df36791550a703f5b0b","tid":1774480,"uid":59461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T12:06:30.000Z","msg":"寫左最重要係用黎記錄自已點柒，跟着先有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0dff68b7138ac02e82afeb2e417af4cfb4dfb56","tid":1774480,"uid":269753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T12:44:27.000Z","msg":"寫左先, 到時自然會有人討論<br />\n不過唔好想得太理想, 可能係會有高手, 但亦可能有假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d39c9ad99ce700b9496323768b4a81182703614","tid":1774480,"uid":308853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45db7df0cd9e8c9de0a5bfcdd4f8dbedc81d4e46","tid":1774480,"uid":57796,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T12:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T23:42:36.000Z","msg":"又係喎。想做就做。"},{"pid":"10c350ab4fc0ecfa71de6a1fbbfe80290bdbf74b","tid":1774480,"uid":254158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:51:4